text.section:
The following persons are not required to obtain a license under this section:
A person licensed by the Department to catch finfish or shellfish for sale;
A retail market, restaurant, or other establishment where finfish or shellfish are sold or served to ultimate consumers, and not for resale;
A person who buys finfish or shellfish for personal use or consumption; and
A person who catches and sells as bait finfish or shellfish species defined as bait under subsection (c) of this section.
